trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat"></xref> objects within a control designer.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션을 나타냅니다 <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat"> </xref> 컨트롤 디자이너에 있는 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스는 상속 될 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class and any derived class defines the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> property as a DesignerAutoFormatCollection object.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>클래스 및 파생된 클래스 정의 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>속성 DesignerAutoFormatCollection 개체로 반환 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Control developers can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> property in a derived control designer, add custom automatic formatting styles, and return the collection of supported formats to the visual designer.
trans-unit.target: 컨트롤 개발자는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>파생된 컨트롤 디자이너 속성을 사용자 지정 자동 서식 지정 스타일을 추가 하 고 비주얼 디자이너로 지원 되는 형식의 컬렉션을 반환 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>

trans-unit.source: The collection dynamically increases as objects are added.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션 개체를 추가할 때를 동적으로 증가 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Indexes in this collection are zero-based.
trans-unit.target: 이 컬렉션의 인덱스는&0;부터 시작 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A> property to determine how many automatic style formats are in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A>속성 컬렉션에 있는 개수 자동 스타일 형식 확인을.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, use the DesignerAutoFormatCollection methods and properties to provide the following functionality: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Add%2A> method to add a single format to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 또한 다음과 같은 기능을 제공 하도록 DesignerAutoFormatCollection 메서드 및 속성을 사용:- <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Add%2A>단일 형식 컬렉션에 추가 하는 방법을.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Insert%2A> method to add a format at a particular index within the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Insert%2A>메서드를 컬렉션 내에서 특정 인덱스에 형식을 추가 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Insert%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Remove%2A> method to remove a format.

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.RemoveAt%2A> method to remove the format at a particular index.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.RemoveAt%2A>메서드 특정 인덱스에서 형식을 제거 하려면.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.RemoveAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Contains%2A> method to determine whether a particular format is already in the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Contains%2A>메서드는 특정 형식 컬렉션에 이미 있는지 여부를 확인 하려면.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Contains%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A> method to retrieve the index of a format within the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A>컬렉션에 있는 서식의 인덱스를 검색 하는 메서드입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Item%2A> property to get or set the format at a particular index, using array notation.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Item%2A>가져오거나 형식을 배열 표기법을 사용 하 여 특정 인덱스에 설정할 속성입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Clear%2A> method to remove all formats from the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Clear%2A>메서드를 컬렉션에서 서식을 모두 제거 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Clear%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A> property to determine the number of formats in the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A>속성 컬렉션에서 형식의 수를 결정 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A> method to get the position of a format within the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A>메서드를 컬렉션에 있는 서식의 위치를 가져옵니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection.IndexOf%2A>

trans-unit.target: 첫 번째 요소는 인덱스 컬렉션 인덱스가&0;부터 시작 하기 때문에 `0` 마지막 요소는 인덱스 및 `Count-1`합니다.

trans-unit.target: 최소 크기는 200 x 200 픽셀입니다.
